    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1929-11-21T00:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1929-11-21T00:00:00-05:00" n="484"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d484">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.00/10624: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Consul General at Canton</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Jenkins</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Extract]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Canton</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1929-11-21T13:00:00+08:00"
                            >November 21, 1929—1 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received November 22—8:45 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Referring to my telegram of November 20, noon. U.S.S. <hi rend="italic"
                        >Mindanao</hi> has arrived Wuchow and reports that Standard Oil Company
                    lighter <hi rend="italic">Denver</hi> has been released and company’s premises
                    cleared of troops. Also that Cantonese troops have entirely evacuated Wuchow and
                    the city is without protection until Kwangsi forces arrive, probably not before
                    the 23rd. <hi rend="italic">Mindanao</hi> is remaining at inner Wuchow for the
                    present. …</p>
                <p rend="center">. . . . . . . . . . . . . .</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Jenkins</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
